# moblies-shop — UI/UX Design System

**Last updated:** 2026-06-22

---

## Typography

### What changed
- **Tajawal** (Arabic) + **Inter** (Latin) via `next/font/google`
- Replaced earlier Geist and IBM Plex Sans Arabic
- RTL body uses Tajawal first; LTR uses Inter first

### Where applied
- `app/layout.tsx` — font loading
- `app/globals.css` — `--font-sans` token chain

### Why / impact
- Tajawal: clean modern Arabic UI font, good readability for POS and tables
- Inter: standard SaaS Latin companion

### PDF (separate from UI fonts)
- Invoice PDF uses **Noto Sans Arabic** (`public/fonts/`) — registered in `lib/pdf/register-fonts.ts`
- Never use Helvetica for Arabic PDF text

---

## Money Display

`formatMoney()` in `lib/utils.ts`:
- Whole numbers: `200` not `200.00`
- Latin digits (`numberingSystem: "latn"`)
- Use in all UI tables, cards, POS, reports

---

## Color System (SaaS Neutral Palette)

- Primary: indigo `#4f46e5` (light) / `#818cf8` (dark)
- Semantic tokens: `--success`, `--warning`, `--destructive` with tinted badge backgrounds
- Subtle borders: `border-border/60`

### Where applied
- `app/globals.css`
- `components/ui/badge.tsx`
- `components/dashboard/stat-card.tsx`

---

## Spacing & Layout Shell

- `--sidebar-width: 16.5rem`, `--header-height: 3.75rem`
- `.app-shell-main` — subtle indigo radial gradient
- `.page-container` — max-width 1400px
- Sticky header with backdrop blur
- **Sidebar:** `h-screen sticky` — logout + theme toggle always visible (no scroll-to-find)

### Where applied
- `app/(dashboard)/layout.tsx` — passes `shopName` from `ShopSettings` to Sidebar/Header
- `components/layout/sidebar.tsx`
- `components/layout/header.tsx`
- `components/layout/mobile-menu-sheet.tsx`

### Shop branding
- **Shop name** from `ShopSettings.shopName` — NOT from `messages/*/app.nameShort`
- Logo from `ShopSettings.logoUrl` (uploaded to `public/uploads/`)

---

## Navigation UX

### Sidebar groups
Main, Inventory, Operations, Analytics, Administration

### Mobile bottom nav
Dashboard, POS, **Sales**, Customers — icon pill on active tab

### Header
- User name + role badge
- Logout + theme toggle icons (desktop)
- Language switcher: segmented pill (AR / EN)

### Permission-gated nav
- `adminOnly`: users, settings
- `accountantOnly`: purchases, expenses

### Where applied
- `components/layout/nav-config.ts`
- `components/layout/sidebar.tsx`
- `components/layout/mobile-bottom-nav.tsx`
- `components/layout/language-switcher.tsx`
- `messages/ar.json`, `messages/en.json` — `nav.groups.*`

---

## POS UI (`app/(dashboard)/pos/pos-client.tsx`)

### Layout
- Category tabs (from product categories in DB)
- Product grid cards (tap to add to cart)
- Search bar above grid
- Cart panel: qty edit, remove, customer select
- **Quick payment buttons:** Cash | Card | On Account (not dropdown)
- Complete sale → redirect to invoice page

### Category labels
- DB stores English category names (Samsung, Apple...)
- Arabic display via `messages/*/pos.categoryNames.*`

---

## UI Primitives (components/ui/)

### Button (`button.tsx`)
- Rounded-lg, shadow-sm on primary, `loading` prop with spinner
- **`asChild`:** spinner NOT passed to Slot children (fixes sale detail crash)

### Card, Table, Dialog, Tabs, Badge, Input, Label
- See prior conventions: rounded-xl cards, muted table headers, pill tabs, semantic badges

