## New Reusable Components

| Component | Path | Purpose |
|-----------|------|---------|
| `DataTableShell` | `components/ui/data-table-shell.tsx` | Bordered table + footer count |
| `FormSection` | `components/ui/form-section.tsx` | Grouped form fields |
| `LoadingSpinner` | `components/ui/loading-spinner.tsx` | Loading indicator |
| `EmptyState` | `components/ui/empty-state.tsx` | Zero-result views |

### List page pattern
```tsx
<DataTableShell footer={`${items.length} items`}>
  <Table>...</Table>
</DataTableShell>
```

