## Page-Level Patterns

| Page | Pattern |
|------|---------|
| Dashboard | Stat cards, EmptyState, quick links |
| Products | DataTableShell, tabular-nums prices |
| **Sales** `/sales` | Date filter card, summary stats, line-item detail in table |
