## RTL / LTR Rules

1. Use **logical properties**: `ms-*`, `me-*`, `ps-*`, `pe-*`, `start-*`, `end-*`, `text-start`, `text-end`
2. Never `text-left` / `text-right` on table headers — use `text-start`
3. Directional icons: `rtl-flip` when needed
4. Arabic headings: no negative letter-spacing

---

## Do NOT (UI layer)

- Do NOT hardcode shop name — read from `ShopSettings` via layout props
- Do NOT remove `touch-manipulation` or 16px mobile input rule
- Do NOT use hardcoded English — use next-intl
- Do NOT use `text-left`/`margin-left` — use logical equivalents
- Do NOT force `.00` on whole numbers in display

---

## When Adding New UI

1. Reuse tokens from `globals.css`
2. Wrap tables in `DataTableShell`
3. Use `EmptyState` for zero results
4. Use `PageHeader` for page titles
5. Use `Button loading={pending}` for async actions
6. Use `formatMoney()` for all currency display
7. **Update this file** with what/why/where/impact
